  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-body">
                <div class="field-content">SoftLayer Private Clouds bring users dedicated cloud solutions featuring a ready-to-use infrastructure. Each Private Cloud that is provisioned provides users will full access to manage and configure their Cloud as they see fit, while providing an environment free from outside user latency and security risks. Private Clouds are provisioned within hours and virtual machines are available in on demand. Consistent with all our services, Private Clouds may be provisioned as a stand-alone solution with the option of integrating all your other SoftLayer solutions and services. Object Storage comes standard with all of our Private Clouds.</div>
